      <h3>What is MYLO?</h3>
      <p>
        MYLO is an application that allows you to automate Reddcoin payments. The payments can be recurring or once-off.
      </p>
      <h3>What are recipients?</h3>
      <p>
        Recepients are simply labels that represent Reddcoin addresses. It's much easier to remember names than it is to remember Reddcoin addresses. 
      </p>
      <h3>What are subscriptions?</h3>
      <p>
        Subscriptions are recurring payments to recipients. You can create daily, weekly, monthly, and annual subscriptions. 
      </p>
      <h3>At what time of the day are my subscriptions fulfilled?</h3>
      <p>
        We send out workers once a day, and they sequentially process all due subscriptions. Depending on the number of suscriptions to process, this can take a while; so there's no exact time.
      </p>
      <h3>X is not working, whats's up with that?</h3>
      <p>
        MYLO is under active development and is currently alpha (pre beta). There will be bugs. The will be problems. Whilst we get notified of any problems, feel free to report them to us on the Github issues page.
      </p>
      <h3>How does the scheduler work?</h3>
      <p>
        The scheduler does exactly what you would expect it to; it allows you to schedule the transfer of Reddcoins to one of your recipients.
      </p>
      <h3>How much does it cost?</h3>
      <p>MYLO charges 1% of all transactions..... for now. This may change when we leave alpha, but we will let you know in plenty of time.</p>
